</span></p><p class="sc-dQEsWe kFLVLU pf-209_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fFlofg cnCjdX pf-211_">These efforts aren’t just symbolic—they reduce urban heat, absorb CO₂, regenerate ecosystems, and inspire lifelong environmental commitment. The sheer scale of participation reveals that citizens worldwide are not only aware of the planetary emergency—they are actively participating in its resolution. It’s a resounding counterpoint to despair: the world is ready.












