</span></p><img alt="Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp__PID:71fef6fa-0c7a-42ed-9ed9-5f697a81c686" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/Earth-day-planet-in-hands.webp?v=1745346025&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:0.75" width="3264" height="4352" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-kMriOJ jsCfBi pf-221_" store="[object Object]"/><p class="sc-dQEsWe kFLVLU pf-222_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fFlofg cnCjdX pf-224_"><font color="#c4874a">Picture by: Margot Richard.&nbsp;</font></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide pf-hide" style="--c-xs:3;--c-sm:2;--c-md:6;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fsvrPk ezIRGP pf-225_ pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-226_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><strong>Glossary<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);">keywords</span></strong><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);"></span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);"></span></span></h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-228_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Carbon Sinks:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Forests/oceans absorbing CO₂; deforestation erodes their capacity.
   



</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-230_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Circular Production:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Designing products for reuse/recycling to minimize waste (e.g., textile recycling)


</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-232_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>CO₂ at 420 ppm:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Record atmospheric carbon dioxide levels, accelerating climate change.</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-234_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>EU Green Deal:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Mandate for 65% textile reuse/recycling by 2030 to combat waste.
   



</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-236_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Fast Fashion:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">High-speed, low-cost clothing production contributing to 10% of global carbon emissions and massive waste.</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-238_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>High Seas Treaty (2023):  </strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);"> UN agreement protecting 60% of oceans outside national control, backed by open science.








</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-240_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Microplastics:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Tiny plastic particles from synthetic fabrics, accounting for 35% of ocean pollution.


</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-242_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Open Science:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Democratized access to research (57% of studies now open-access), aiding climate advocacy.
   



</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-244_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong> Our Power, Our Planet:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);"> 2025 theme emphasizing collective action to expand renewable energy and climate justice. 


</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-246_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Sustainable Fashion:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Ethical production prioritizing circularity, non-toxic materials, and transparency to reduce environmental harm.

</span></p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-248_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Trump Tariffs (2025):</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">155% U.S. tariffs on Chinese imports, impacting fast fashion and sparking trade tensions.
 
